682
00:40:13,590 --> 00:40:15,110
Luo Jida?

683
00:40:16,551 --> 00:40:18,951
Isn't he the father
of that wicked woman, Luo Ailian?

684
00:40:20,150 --> 00:40:25,511
Why is Danqing
keeping her father's memorial tablet?

685
00:40:29,871 --> 00:40:31,351
And who is Bin?

